<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Skirr" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Skirr,</orth> to move rapidly, to scour: <cit><quote>make them s. away,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 64</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>s. the country round,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.3.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 3, 35</bibl></cit> (== round the country).
